SQL Essential Training is designed to help users understand the most common language for database wrangling, SQL. All the examples in SQLiteStudio, an intuitive and easy-to-install database manager. All the major features of SQL: creating tables; defining relationships; manipulating strings, numbers, and dates; using triggers to automate actions; and using subselects and views. Course offers a solid working knowledge of the language and shows how to retrieve and manage data efficiently. 
